  <summary date="2022-04-01T20:27:49Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Cutting Rampant Access to Crack Kits Act of 2022 or the CRACK Act of 2022

This bill prohibits community-based overdose prevention programs, syringe services programs, and other harm reduction programs from using funds made available through the American Rescue Plan Act of 2021 to procure or distribute pipes or other paraphernalia that can be used to smoke, inhale, or ingest narcotics.</summary>
